{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "021eeef6-77c9-4c73-8402-7bcc33d526f3",
    "name": "assessment-todo-api",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for the Assessment Todo List API.\n\n**Setup:**\n\n1. Import this collection AND the environment file (assessment-todo-api.postman_environment.json).\n    \n2. Select the **assessment-todo-api-local** environment.\n    \n3. Run **Register** → **Verify Email** (paste code from Mailtrap) → **Login** (token auto-saves).\n    \n4. All protected endpoints use `{{token}}` automatically.\n    \n\nEvery response follows the `GlobalApiResponse` envelope:\n\n``` json\n{\n  \"_metadata\": { \"outcome\": \"SUCCESS\", \"outcomeCode\": 0, \"numOfRecords\": 1, \"message\": \"...\" },\n  \"records\": { ... },\n  \"errors\": []\n}\n\n ```",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "24757755",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/24757755-021eeef6-77c9-4c73-8402-7bcc33d526f3?source=collection_link"
  },
